snippet.title: N64 Hey You! Pikachu COMMERCIAL
snippet.description:
Hey You! Pikachu was released for the Nintendo 64.  This one's kinda long. 
I'm too young to know for sure, but I bet the microphone for this game didn't work too well.  Viewers, what were your experiences with it?
